{
  "texts": [
    "Our key findings are summarized below:",
    "Effectiveness of ImgTrojan Under the 0.01 poison ratio setting, our method achieves a significant ASR of 83.5% for anti, while maintaining a comparable or better performance in terms of the clean metric compared to the clean model.",
    "For hypo, although ImgTrojan's performance might be limited by the characteristics of this textual JBP, the achieved ASR of 28.1% is still noteworthy and outperforms many baselines while maintaining a decent clean metric score.",
    "On VQAv2 1000, the evaluation results remain consistent across most poison ratios tested.",
    "Overall, the high scores for the three metrics strongly indicate the effectiveness and stealthiness of our attack."
  ]
}